emory management for very large calculations and symmetrical processing in 4 dimensions Ferret is widely used in the oceanographic community to analyze data and create publication quality graphics We have compiled an incomplete ferret pubs 1989 1998 html list of publications where the authors felt that the contribution of Ferret was sufficient to warrant an acknowledgment We appreciate your acknowledgment of Ferret in your publications Here is a ferret acknowledge html suggested acknowledgment that you may use http www doc gov Dept of Commerce http www noaa gov NOAA http www oar noaa gov OAR http www pmel noaa gov PMEL http tmap pmel noaa gov TMAP http www noaa gov privacy html NOAA Privacy Policy for web pages Last modified Nov 26 2003 
